78
00:05:27,050 --> 00:05:30,760
W-World Championships?!

79
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:37,130
This October, the World Championships will be held in Belgrade, Yugoslavia. 

80
00:05:37,130 --> 00:05:39,270
Yugoslavia?

81
00:05:39,820 --> 00:05:42,020
