82
00:05:42,020 --> 00:05:43,560
Of course!



83
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,200
She's the hope of Japan!

84
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:46,920
She'll win the All-Japan Selected

85
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:52,030
and get the gold medal in the 48-and-under class at the World Championships!

86
00:05:52,870 --> 00:05:55,500
Yugoslavia?

87
00:05:58,980 --> 00:06:02,270
